 Extra Mural Lecture  201617

 presents

 '25 Years of E2B9eforms'

 a talk by

 Shri. P Chidambaram

 Former Finance Minister, Govt. of India

 Date Saturday, November 5th

 Venue: Student Activity Center (SAC), IIT Madras

 Time: 10:15 am onwards


 Speaker Profile:


 Palaniappan Chidambaram is a Member of Parliament  Rajya Sabha and a
 former Union Minister of Finance of India. Mr Chidambaram was a corporate
 lawyer and an important member of the last Congressled government. He ha
s
 also been the Home Minister, in the wake of the 2008 Mumbai terror attack
s.
 As a Finance Minister, Mr Chidambaram brought discipline in government
 spending and launched an ambitious tax reform program to tackle an unwiel
dy
 fiscal deficit. He has been credited with taking the bold decision of
 prioritizing elections above corporate demands to deploy security for
 T2020 matches of IPL. He did his MBA from Harvard Business School and
 practiced law in the Supreme Court and various High Courts of India.

 You can ask all your questions to Shri P Chidambaram. Fill this form
  to get your questions listed in
 Q&A session of 5 November, Saturday

